rs of neurons not directly connected due to the\nbrain's sparsity, firing-rate and interspike-intervals codes would be the most\nefficient codes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Sep 2017 16:44:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 5 Oct 2018 09:58:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 17 Oct 2018 15:50:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-18"}
