eq$ 5/3 to q=1 when $\\alpha$ increases from zero to $\\alpha \\simeq 1$,\nand remains q = 1 thereafter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Sep 2017 21:28:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-22"}
