erated from\npolymorphic WannaCry copies, on which 63 (of 63 tested) anti-virus (AV)\nproducts fail.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Sep 2017 23:38:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-27"}
